queries: select tzc.partition_date as fecha_proceso, 'R10063102' as cod_incidencia, count(*) as num_reg_total, sum(case when tzc.g7015_fecdesde <= tzc.g7015_fec_has then 0 else 1 end) as num_reg_error, from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) as op_timestamp, 'bi_corp_bdr.jm_trz_cliente' as tabla from bi_corp_bdr.jm_trz_cliente tzc where tzc.partition_date = '${month_partition_bdr}' group by tzc.partition_date

select tzc.partition_date as fecha_proceso, 'R10103102' as cod_incidencia, count(*) as num_reg_total, sum(case when tzc.g7015_idnumcli is null then 1 else 0 end ) as num_reg_error, from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) as op_timestamp, 'bi_corp_bdr.jm_trz_cliente' as tabla from bi_corp_bdr.jm_trz_cliente tzc left join (select distinct cbi.g4093_idnumcli from bi_corp_bdr.jm_client_bii cbi ) cbi on tzc.g7015_idnumcli = cbi.g4093_idnumcli where tzc.partition_date = '${month_partition_bdr}' group by tzc.partition_date
